doc.after: The Robert V Fullerton Museum of Art located on the campus of California State University San Bernardino contains a collection of Egyptian antiquities ancient pottery from present day Italy and funerary art from ancient China In addition to the extensive antiquities on display the museum presents contemporary art and changing exhibitions
